Requirements
============

Python 2.7 (for twitter package), Django 1.9, PostgreSQL (for upsert).

Install
=======

First, copy local.sh.example to local.sh and fill it with your credentials.
Then, source local.sh

Then, pip install the repo.

Then, provision the database and create an admin::

    buzzdetect migrate
    buzzdetect createsuperuser

Usage
=====

Follow your twitter stream to create tweets::

    buzzdetect twitter_stream

Log retweets, run this command every minute or so::

    buzzdetect twitter_retweets

Run the development server::

    buzzdetect runserver
